  "remarks": "YEi.009. Title: Major General. Designation: Commander of the Houthi’s Fifth Military Region. A prominent leader of Houthi forces and commander of forces in Hudaydah, Hajjah, Al Mahwit, and Raymah, Yemen – threatening the peace, security, and stability of Yemen. As of 2021, Al-Madani was assigned to the offensive targeting Marib.; Listing: Listed by the 2140 Committee on 9 November 2021",
